data.description: Welcome home to the highly desirable Kekuilani Subdivision! This spacious 3 bed/2.5 bath contemporary style nicely upgraded single family home located at the beginning of the cul-de-sac features upgraded kitchen with quartz countertops, modern backsplash, updated bathrooms, Pergo Koa/porcelain tile flooring throughout the house, plantation shutters, modern style fans & much more. Updated garage with AC wall unit & extra insulation! Home also features a fully fenced private yard great for entertainment and relaxation. Conveniently located within close proximity to schools, neighborhood parks, Ka Makana Ali'i Mall, restaurants, shopping centers, golf course, beaches, freeway access, and much more!
